sudo apt update
sudo apt install lxc lxc-templates

To create a new LXC container: 

sudo lxc-create -n mycontainer -t debian

Start the container: 

sudo lxc-start -n mycontainer

Access the container: 

sudo lxc-attach -n mycontainer



Resource limits: Edit the container's configuration file (/var/lib/lxc/mycontainer/config) to set resource limits:

lxc.cgroup.memory.limit_in_bytes = 512M
lxc.cgroup.cpu.shares = 512



Network configuration: Set up a bridge for containers:

lxc.net.0.type = veth
lxc.net.0.link = lxcbr0
lxc.net.0.flags = up
lxc.net.0.hwaddr = 00:16:3e:xx:xx:xx

